						               													<description>Chaos Kingdoms is a high fantasy board game with an immersive world map. Players take on the role of adventuring Heroes, each with their own set of unique skills and strange character. A Faction of cohorts carry the Hero&amp;rsquo;s flag, lending their own abilities to their leader. There are 3 legendary goals before them: Last Man Standing, Immortality or Godhood. As they advance, players vanquish rival Heroes, explore dungeons, and spike their power with experience &amp;amp; plunder.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to WIN:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For lively game play, there are 3 ways to win. &amp;#10;Last Man Standing: PVP, Player Elimination&amp;#10;Immortality: Battle 4 Jabberwockies to get 4 artifact pieces that grant Immortality&amp;#10;Godhood: Build 5 glorious shrines to yourself in 5 cities&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game play is relatively simple, making it an easy-entry game for novices. There are 12 Heroes and 12 Factions to choose from, which provides a multitude of strategic combinations. Roll a six-sided dice to travel a classic RPG hex map. Boldly engage with monsters and villains in dungeons and lairs. Battles are a contest of attack rolls with modifiers from pulsing Magic Items and burning Spells. Once powerful enough, conquer fellow Heroes, claim Immortality, or climb into the vaulted existence of a God.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Features include:&amp;#10;A multitude of different Hero / Faction combinations&amp;#10;Exploring Dungeons, Ruins, Caves, Hideouts, Towers &amp;amp; more&amp;#10;Unique Artifacts, Weapons &amp;amp; Spells&amp;#10;Fierce PVP and long range attacks&amp;#10;Stealing (very fun and effective)&amp;#10;Targeting opponent Cities&amp;#10;Targeting opponent Items and Followers&amp;#10;Goal: PVP Last Man Standing&amp;#10;Goal: Immortality / Jabberwockies&amp;#10;Goal: Godhood / Shrines&amp;#10;Ruling the World of Chaos Kingdoms&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
